request.description:
Login with email and password. Returns nested token structure with access and refresh tokens including expiration times. Rate limited to 5 requests per 15 minutes.

Response format:
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "user": { "id": "...", "email": "...", "role": "..." },
    "tokens": {
      "access": { "token": "...", "expiresAt": "..." },
      "refresh": { "token": "...", "expiresAt": "..." }
    }
  }
}
```

Refresh access token using refresh token. Returns new access and refresh tokens with expiration times. Rate limited to 5 requests per 15 minutes.

Response format:
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "tokens": {
      "access": { "token": "...", "expiresAt": "..." },
      "refresh": { "token": "...", "expiresAt": "..." }
    }
  }
}
```

